{"tid":1335193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[721] 咁都忍得 屎都食得啦！ 聽日哂佢冷 香港人今次嬲到仆街呀","createTime":"2019-07-20T11:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T13:00:56.000Z","uid":231206,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0ab948476bf2694914c979149878089ad153770d","tid":1335193,"uid":231206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"致所有同道:<br />\n<br />\n狗官 警犬 藍絲廢中廢老 支耶團<br />\n<br />\n每日都做咁撚多閪野<br />\n<br />\n喂  <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁都忍得 屎都食得啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n識嬲嘅 如果聽日仲唔行出黎 後日呢班垃圾就會更加過份<br />\n香港已經危急到無free rider嘅餘地 殺到埋身啦！<br />\n<br />\nMemo紙都撕一貼十<br />\n人 你打一個 我地企返十個出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地一齊哂佢冷！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人今次係堅嬲 對住呢班垃圾 我地已經乜都做得出<br />\n<br />\n要佢地知道 做埋啲閪野到底要承受幾恐怖嘅怒火！"},{"pid":"377d78e5d3c626f176133b8ad2121aff06abb065","tid":1335193,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[沙盤推演] 大家有無諗過呢場抗爭既end game係點?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1334346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1334346</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f6b586c2d0c5a2b158b729963fc02037c462d239","tid":1335193,"uid":41576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gdOn17k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgdOn17k.png&h=0fcc44a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0eb0dd907bf0509efc3c090de2c9d7037056f03c","tid":1335193,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.g